        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2040170510" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9092938223202447018">It’s my first time reading Anthony, and overall I enjoyed this story. Yes, it’s dated, &amp; yep definitely some unnecessary female sexualization, but overall I liked the story and it was a fun read juxtaposed with my current political read. I liked the play of good verses evil and all the grey areas, the exploration of original sin, and what if bad things are done for good reasons. It was a bit too simple in some places, but overall interesting read.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


