           <span class="uitext reviewText">fans of humorous fantasy</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/289556-jackie-the-librarian?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
