              <span id="reviewTextContainer10673823" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4255030557465886634">This was a neat new take for a fantasy subject &amp; blended some light SF as well. I really enjoyed it, although the series got a bit redundant for me after several books. I did finish &amp; keep the series. I reread it a year or two ago &amp; would recommend it. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

